[A_Creature_Shark_upregate H7Creature]
mName="Wanizame"
mLore="For Shark Guards, the title of Wanizame is a recognition of their valor and dependability, while their savage brethren embody the true meaning of this word. Shark Warriors consider their main weapon to be the one bestowed on them by nature itself - sharp teeth which tear the flesh of victims. The status of a fighter in the tribe depends on the number of defeated enemies, and the stronger they were, the more honor he receives. After earning the right to become a Wanizame, a warrior covers his body with battle tattoos and his bloodlust becomes truly unquenchable."

