[A_Creature_Shark H7Creature]
mName="Shark Warrior"
mLore="During the creation of new types of Beastmen, the Wizards from House Chimera experimented with different types of animals, intending to bestow the most suitable talents on their creations. Unlike Shark Guards, Shark Warriors were created from sand sharks that roamed the Sahaar Desert with the same ease as their sea brethren swam through the deep waters. Thanks to their ability to move unhindered under almost any surface, these Beastmen could be of great use to the Seven Cities, if not for their wild unbridled temper. Neither the Wizards nor the Nagas of Hashima were able to subdue these unruly creatures, and only the inhabitants of Shanria were able to find some way to approach them."

